# Our environment

We have tested this bug on Dovecot-Core 2.3.10, and our configuration is:

```
# 2.3.10 (): dovecot.conf
# OS: Linux 4.15.0-96-generic x86_64 Ubuntu 18.04.1 LTS
# Hostname: ubuntu
